&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform Architect&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HG Insights - Remote, Brazil&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;HG Insights is a B2B market intelligence and Go-To-Market (GTM) analytics platform. We provide sales, marketing, and revenue operations teams with actionable data about what technologies companies are using (technographics), how much they spend on IT, and when they are likely to buy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HG Insights is seeking a versatile and experienced Platform Architect. The ideal candidate will bring a strong mix of technical expertise, leadership experience, and a proven track record in building scalable distributed systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Platform Architect to drive technical excellence, mentor teams, and lead the development of our next-generation products.&lt;br&gt;The role requires someone who can balance strategic thinking with hands-on technical leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Responsible For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
