&lt;li&gt;Lead and mentor engineering teams across frontend, backend, and infrastructure domains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive technical vision and architecture decisions for complex distributed systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with executive leadership on product strategy and technical roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and scale engineering teams through effective hiring, mentoring, and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish engineering best practices, processes, and quality standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive innovation in cloud-native architectures and deployment strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead implementation of cost-effective and performant cloud solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee development of scalable frontend and backend systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage site operations and technical infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
