&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;20+ years of software engineering experience with at least 5 years in leadership roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience in cloud-native technologies, distributed systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of leading full-stack engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in modern frontend and backend technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with cloud platforms and infrastructure management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong background in API design and microsfervices architecture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with monitoring, observability, and performance optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of successful product deliveries and team scaling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
